crossAccountModelRegisterRoleArn.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the SageMaker model registry account. Required only to register model versions created by a different SageMaker Canvas AWS account than the AWS account in which SageMaker model registry is set up.

status.description: Describes whether the integration to the model registry is enabled or disabled in the Canvas application. Valid values are `ENABLED` and `DISABLED`.
